(811, 1, '2021-06-02 23:11:41', '2021-06-02 22:11:41', '[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][thb_page_menu menu=\"149\"][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][thb_accordion accordion=\"true\" tabs_scroll=\"\"][vc_tta_section title=\"What does The Reloved Rack do?\" tab_id=\"1581952178992-0dce887d-fbba\"][vc_column_text]We are a Lagos based consignment store that resells new and preloved authentic designer items with emphasis on authentic.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"What if I don\'t like the item after purchase?\" tab_id=\"1581952179006-053caf4b-369d\"][vc_column_text]We ask that you please ensure to ask all the questions required to reduce incidents of return.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Do you do refunds?\" tab_id=\"1581952417211-2bbc4427-30ae\"][vc_column_text]Yes we do. We also offer store credits.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Are all your items authentic?\" tab_id=\"1622659530314-3469aeee-9426\"][vc_column_text]ALL items listed on our page are authentic.Our premium designer items are third party authenticated. We also trace the source of the initial purchase to ensure it is of authentic roots.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Is bargaining allowed?\" tab_id=\"1622671780951-a99937cf-7cae\"][vc_column_text]Our prices are already at a discount but you are welcome to make us a counter offer on our pre-owned items. Our brand new item prices are fixed.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/thb_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Frequently Asked Questions', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '50-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-06-02 23:11:41', '2021-06-02 22:11:41', '', 50, 'https://therelovedrack.com/?p=811', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
