(772, 1, '2021-06-02 19:35:47', '2021-06-02 18:35:47', '[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][thb_page_menu menu=\"149\"][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">THANK YOU FOR YOUR INTEREST IN THE RELOVED RACK (TRR)</strong>\n\nThis document sets out the terms under which TRR will engage with you, the Consignor. This information is STRICTLY confidential and must not be distributed to any third party, in whole or part, without TRR\'s express permission.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">CONSIGNING WITH US</strong>\n\nTRR will work with you to declutter your closet, sort through items and advise you on the items that can be resold. This will be done based on the quality, condition of use, brand and original purchase price of each item.\n\nItems in order of preference are bags, shoes, articles of clothing and accessories including sunglasses, jewelry etc. We would accept new and pre-owned bags and shoes in good condition however, all defects must be disclosed and assessed before acceptance.\n\nFor clothing, we will only be accepting items that are brand new or less than 6 months of use. All used clothing must be dry-cleaned, used jewelry must be sanitized using rubbing alcohol or other effective disinfectants. All leather goods may be polished without changing their original condition.\n\nPlease include original packaging of all items where available. This includes: shoe boxes, dust bags, dry cleaner\'s bags for clothes etc.\n\nTRR reserves the right to determine which goods will be accepted for listing on the site.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">PRICING</strong>\n\nPricing is determined by the Consignor. TRR will advise on the pricing of each item based on current market value and condition of the item. Final agreed price will be inclusive of our commission.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">FEES &amp; COMMISSION</strong>\n\nTRR will take a percentage commission on each item or on the sum total of items sold on behalf of the Consignor as follows:\n<ul>\n 	<li>High Street Brands: New - 25%; Used - 30%</li>\n 	<li>Premium Designer: New - 20%; Used - 22%</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">STORAGE &amp; STORAGE FEES</strong>\n\nTRR will hold inventory for each Consignor for a maximum of 4 weeks or 30 days* at no cost - 0% storage fees. Any unsold item MUST be returned to the Consignor at the end of this period.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">PAYMENT</strong>\n\nTRR will process payment for all sold items to the Consignor a week after receipt of payment from the buyer.\n\nAll remittances shall be made per item sold or lumped together as a single payment where multiple items are sold at the same time.\n\nAny deviation from this must be agreed in writing with the Consignor prior to listing of accepted items on the site.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"80px\"][vc_column_text]<small>*Requests for extended storage periods may be granted at TRR\'s discretion for a fee.</small>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Terms & Conditions (Consignors)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '710-autosave-v1', '', '', '2021-06-02 19:35:47', '2021-06-02 18:35:47', '', 710, 'https://therelovedrack.com/?p=772', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
