(321, 1, '2020-02-21 13:24:32', '2020-02-21 13:24:32', '<p>[vc_row thb_scroll_bottom=\"true\" thb_scroll_bottom_color=\"light\" css=\".vc_custom_1582626279264{padding-top: 6vh !important;padding-bottom: 12vh !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1538731770774{padding-right: 5% !important;}\"][vc_column_text]I have an obsession with details and pattern. My dresses are very reasonably priced, for dresses that are cut on the body. I am convinced that you dont need to spend a fortune to look like a million. Go to a place where youre not going to be stressed, because a honeymoon itself can be a stressful thing. I want people to be afraid of the women I dress.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1538731695960{padding-left: 5% !important;}\"][vc_column_text]I am no longer concerned with sensation and innovation, but with the perfection of my style. A woman is never sexier than when she is comfortable in her clothes. Doing collections, doing fashion is like a non-stop dialogue. I am not interested in shock tactics. I just want to make beautiful clothes.<br />\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row thb_full_width=\"true\" thb_row_padding=\"true\" thb_column_padding=\"true\" thb_scroll_bottom=\"true\" thb_scroll_bottom_color=\"light\" css=\".vc_custom_1582626930359{padding-top: 28vh !important;padding-bottom: 28vh !important;background-color: #0a0a0a !important;}\"][vc_column thb_color=\"thb-light-column\" el_class=\"text-center\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-size: 150%;\">Full Screen Rows</span></h1>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row thb_scroll_bottom=\"true\" thb_scroll_bottom_color=\"light\" css=\".vc_custom_1538731725784{padding-top: 12vh !important;padding-bottom: 12vh !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1538731770774{padding-right: 5% !important;}\"][vc_column_text]I would like to be a one-man multinational fashion phenomenon. I like to be real. I dont like things to be staged or fussy. Fashion fosters cliches of beauty, but I want to tear them apart. I think God is the most fantastic designer. I cant get sucked into that celebrity thing, because I think its just crass.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1538731695960{padding-left: 5% !important;}\"][vc_column_text]Fashions fade, style is eternal. I believe in comfort. If you dont feel comfortable in your clothes, its hard to think of anything else. What you wear is how you present yourself to the world, especially today when human contacts go so fast. Over the years I have learned that what is important in a dress is the woman who is wearing it.<br />\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row thb_row_padding=\"true\" thb_column_padding=\"true\" thb_scroll_bottom=\"true\" thb_scroll_bottom_style=\"style2\" thb_scroll_bottom_color=\"light\" css=\".vc_custom_1582626534759{padding-top: 25vh !important;padding-bottom: 25vh !important;}\" bg_gradient1=\"#3493e5\" bg_gradient2=\"#00ea9c\"][vc_column thb_color=\"thb-light-column\" el_class=\"text-center\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Gradient Backgrounds in</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Different Directions</span></h1>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row thb_scroll_bottom=\"true\" thb_scroll_bottom_color=\"light\" css=\".vc_custom_1538731725784{padding-top: 12vh !important;padding-bottom: 12vh !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]Behold was was darkness Upon. Called let also set behold One fowl fly two firmament subdue he may without divided. Appear signs wont man good face yielding earth great lesser Were darkness. There. Fruit meat. That fifth divide creepeth wont moved of make, likeness. The him over female had given had he called unto you.</p>\n<p>If you cut a painters hands off, hed still feel the urge to pick up a brush. I design from i