(614, 1, '2020-03-11 13:34:50', '2020-03-11 13:34:50', '[vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1583933921244{margin-top: 60px !important;margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h2>Shop Header Styles</h2>\nPeak Shop comes with various different shop &amp; product category category header styles to make your site unique.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row thb_full_width=\"true\" css=\".vc_custom_1583959511942{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}\"][vc_column][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"627\"][/thb_image][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row thb_full_width=\"true\" css=\".vc_custom_1583959597526{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}\"][vc_column][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"628\"][/thb_image][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1583959692603{padding-top: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<ol>\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #121212; font-size: 14px;\">Display Product Category description</span></li>\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #121212; font-size: 14px;\">Display Sub-Category links</span></li>\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #121212; font-size: 14px;\">Set backgrounds &amp; colors and choose between different layouts.</span></li>\n</ol>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1583933921244{margin-top: 60px !important;margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h2>Product Listing Styles</h2>\nPeak Shops comes with 3 unique layouts and 4 different \"Add to Cart\" placements and styles. You can toggle Product Category, Rating, Product Excerpt[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row thb_full_width=\"true\" css=\".vc_custom_1583960879233{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_column][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"636\"][/thb_image][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1583934174521{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"629\"]\n<h5>Filter &amp; Sidebar Styles</h5>\n<small>Choose from Regular, Off-Screen, or Hidden filter options.</small>[/thb_image][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1583934179801{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"630\"]\n<h5>Quantity Styles</h5>\n<small>We have included different quantity styles for different style online shops.</small>[/thb_image][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1583934183927{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"631\"]\n<h5>Product Spacing</h5>\n<small>Adjust product spacing as needed to fit more products or to add more breathing space if you have a low number of products.</small>[/thb_image][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1583934174521{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"634\"]\n<h5>Shop Pagination Styles</h5>\n<small>Different pagination options allows you to change your shop experience as needed.</small>[/thb_image][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1583934179801{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"633\"]\n<h5>Product Badge Styles</h5>\n<small>Different product niches require different styles and our badge styles reflect that.</small>[/thb_image][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1583934183927{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"632\"]\n<h5>Live Search</h5>\n<small>Customers should not waste time searching for products and Live Search displays the most relevant results.</small>[/thb_image][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1583960362391{margin-top: 48px !important;margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h2>Product Layouts &amp; Options</h2>\nPeak Shops comes with 3 unique layouts and sidebar options. You can choose between 4 different tab styles including an accordion style.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row thb_full_width=\"true\" css=\".vc_custom_1583961140700{margin-top: 20px !important;margin-bottom: 48px !important;}\"][vc_column][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"635\"][/thb_image][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1583934174521{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"639\"]\n<h5>Product Tab Styles</h5>\n<small>Peak Shops has 4 different tab styles depending on different product page needs.</small>[/thb_image][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1583934179801{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"638\"]\n<h5>Product Tab Position</h5>\n<small>You might want to change Product Tab Position if you have a larger product description or different number of tabs.</small>[/thb_image][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1583934183927{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"637\"]\n<h5>Product Sidebars</h5>\n<small>Display your product sidebar on the left or the right or just hide it altogether!</small>[/thb_image][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1583934174521{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"645\"]\n<h5>Product Swatches</h5>\n<small>Peak Shops comes with built-in support for WooCommerce swatches, utilizing the core WooCommerce functions.</small>[/thb_image][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1583934179801{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"644\"]\n<h5>WPML Multilanguage &amp; Multicurrency</h5>\n<small>You have nothing to worry about if you are running an International Online Shop. Peak Shops have you covered.</small>[/thb_image][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1583934183927{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"643\"]\n<h5>Product Thumbnail Layouts</h5>\n<small>Change the position of your product thumbnails easily. This way you can adjust your product image size accordingly.</small>[/thb_image][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1583934174521{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"642\"]\n<h5>Catalog Mode</h5>\n<small>Not selling right away? Enable Catalog Mode and showcase your products.</small>[/thb_image][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1583934179801{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"641\"]\n<h5>Product Video</h5>\n<small>With built-in video support, you can attach videos to your products.</small>[/thb_image][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1583934183927{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"640\"]\n<h5>Add to Cart Button Styles</h5>\n<small>4 different Add to Cart buttons, all with different color options.</small>[/thb_image][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Features', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'features', '', '', '2020-03-11 13:34:50', '2020-03-11 13:34:50', '', 0, 'http://peakshops.fuelthemes.net/?page_id=614', 0, 'page', '', 0),
