(802, 1, '2021-06-02 19:08:01', '2021-06-02 18:08:01', '[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][thb_page_menu menu=\"149\"][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]Luxury pieces are an investment and we help secure your investment by guaranteeing each and every item we sell as authentic.\r\n\r\nEach and every piece of our inventory, especially our premium designer items, undergo rigorous internal checks as well as confirmation via 3rd party independent authentication software to give confidence on the authenticity of the item. The process we undergo starts from a thorough visual inspection of hardware, material, craftsmanship, tags, logos, lettering, purchase receipts etc. We also do a side by side comparison of the style and brand and where required, use 3rd party authentication software to give 100% authenticity.\r\n\r\nOnly items proven authentic are accepted for resale.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'How We Authenticate', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '794-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-06-02 19:08:01', '2021-06-02 18:08:01', '', 794, 'https://therelovedrack.com/?p=802', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(803, 1, '2021-06-02 19:13:14', '2021-06-02 18:13:14', '<p>[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][thb_page_menu menu=\"149\"][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">THANK YOU FOR YOUR INTEREST IN THE RELOVED RACK (TRR)</strong></p>\r\n<p>This document sets out the terms under which TRR will engage with you, the Buyer. This information is STRICTLY confidential and must not be distributed to any third party, in whole or part, without TRR\'s express permission.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">QUALITY OF ITEMS</strong></p>\r\n<p>We take utmost care in ensuring that the goods we cell meet a certain standard of quality and this includes checking for any defects, discolorations, peeling etc.</p>\r\n<p>We care for our customers and will bring only the best bargains to you at great quality. Items featured are either brand new or reasonably used preloved goods from previous owners who are decluttering. We maintain a standard of cleanliness to ensure the goods reach you in the best state possible.</p>\r\n<p>We will always disclose the condition of all goods (new or used) and defects (if any) will be highlighted. [/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">PAYMENT</strong></p>\r\n<p>Full payment validates order. Deposits may be accepted on certain items at our discretion on such terms to be agreed in writing.</p>\r\n<p>We only accept payment via electronic channels. Payment details will be provided at checkout.</p>\r\n<p>Each customer is served on a first come, first serve basis and will be given 24 hours to make payment on selected items after which the next customer indicating interest will be invited to make payment for the same item.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">STOCKPILING</strong></p>\r\n<p>TRR may hold paid stock for up to 2 weeks after which we will dispatch to the buyer. Please endeavor to receive goods as soon as payment is made.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">DELIVERY</strong></p>\r\n<p>We deliver nationwide via a multitude of logistics companies. We are amenable to using your choice of courier where required.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">RETURNS &amp; REFUNDS</strong></p>\r\n<p>Returns are accepted on unworn and unused items in the same state as at the time of purchase. Cost of return will be borne by the buyer. Refund will be processed within 48 hours after assessing the returned item. We do not accept exchanges on any sold items. [/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\r\n', 'Terms & Conditions (Buyers)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'terms-conditions-buyers', '', '', '2021-06-02 19:33:15', '2021-06-02 18:33:15', '', 0, 'https://therelovedrack.com/?page_id=803', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(804, 1, '2021-06-02 19:12:08', '2021-06-02 18:12:08', '[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][thb_page_menu menu=\"149\"][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">THANK YOU FOR YOUR INTEREST IN THE RELOVED RACK (TRR)</strong>\r\n\r\nThis document sets out the terms under which TRR will engage with you, the Consignor. This information is STRICTLY confidential and must not be distributed to any third party, in whole or part, without TRR\'s express permission.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">CONSIGNING WITH US</strong>\r\n\r\nTRR will work with you to declutter your closet, sort through items and advise you on the items that can be resold. This will be done based on the quality, condition of use, brand and original purchase price of each item.\r\n\r\nItems in order of preference are bags, shoes, articles of clothing and accessories including sunglasses, jewelry etc. We would accept new and pre-owned bags and shoes in good condition however, all defects must be disclosed and assessed before acceptance.\r\n\r\nFor clothing, we will only be accepting items that are brand new or less than 6 months of use. All used clothing must be dry-cleaned, used jewelry must be sanitized using rubbing alcohol or other effective disinfectants. All leather goods may be polished without changing their original condition.\r\n\r\nPlease include original packaging of all items where available. This includes: shoe boxes, dust bags, dry cleaner\'s bags for clothes etc.\r\n\r\nTRR reserves the right to determine which goods will be accepted for listing on the site.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">PRICING</strong>\r\n\r\nPricing is determined by the Consignor. TRR will advise on the pricing of each item based on current market value and condition of the item. Final agreed price will be inclusive of our commission.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">FEES &amp; COMMISSION</strong>\r\n\r\nTRR will take a percentage commission on each item or on the sum total of items sold on behalf of the Consignor as follows:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>High Street Brands: New - 25%; Used - 30%</li>\r\n 	<li>Premium Designer: New - 20%; Used - 22%</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">STORAGE &amp; STORAGE FEES</strong>\r\n\r\nTRR will hold inventory for each Consignor for a maximum of 4 weeks or 30 days* at no cost - 0% storage fees. Any unsold item MUST be returned to the Consignor at the end of this period.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">PAYMENT</strong>\r\n\r\nTRR will process payment for all sold items to the Consignor a week after receipt of payment from the buyer.\r\n\r\nAll remittances shall be made per item sold or lumped together as a single payment where multiple items are sold at the same time.\r\n\r\nAny deviation from this must be agreed in writing with the Consignor prior to listing of accepted items on the site.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"80px\"][vc_column_text]<small>*Requests for extended storage periods may be granted at TRR\'s discretion for a fee.</small>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Terms & Conditions (Consignors)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '710-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-06-02 19:12:08', '2021-06-02 18:12:08', '', 710, 'https://therelovedrack.com/?p=804', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
