(800, 1, '2021-06-02 19:32:33', '2021-06-02 18:32:33', '<p>[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][thb_page_menu menu=\"149\"][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]Luxury pieces are an investment and we help secure your investment by guaranteeing each and every item we sell as authentic.</p>\n<p>Each and every piece of our inventory, especially our premium designer items, undergo rigorous internal checks as well as confirmation via 3rd party independent authentication software to give confidence on the authenticity of the item. The process we undergo starts from a thorough visual inspection of hardware, material, craftsmanship, tags, logos, lettering, purchase receipts etc. We also do a side by side comparison of the style and brand and where required, use 3rd party authentication software to give 100% authenticity.</p>\n<p>Only items proven authentic are accepted for resale.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\n', 'How We Authenticate', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '794-autosave-v1', '', '', '2021-06-02 19:32:33', '2021-06-02 18:32:33', '', 794, 'https://therelovedrack.com/?p=800', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
