(670, 1, '2020-01-28 14:56:26', '2020-01-28 14:56:26', '[vc_row thb_full_width=\"true\" thb_row_padding=\"true\" thb_column_padding=\"true\" css=\".vc_custom_1582198247050{margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=\"30px\"][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1582024949496{padding-top: 250px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;background-image: url(https://peakshops.fuelthemes.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/a1.jpg?id=262) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_column_inner thb_color=\"thb-light-column\"][vc_column_text]\n<h1>About Peakshops</h1>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1582198694605{margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\" el_class=\"align-justify\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 500;\">It pains me physically to see woman victimized, rendered pathetic by fashion.</span></h2>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"26px\"][vc_column_text]I think in the darkest moments, we need a break. I always say: To be well dressed you must be well naked. I don\'t really know how to do casual clothes. Fashion moves so quickly that, unless you have a strong point of view, you can lose integrity. Men have got more of adiscerning eye. They appreciate <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #c0af8e;\">cut</span> and <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #c0af8e;\">details</span>, things that aren\'t so obvious. I can design a collection in a day and I always do, cause I\'ve always got a load of Italians on my back, moaning that it\'s late. I believe in comfort. If you don\'t feel comfortable in your clothes, it\'s hard to think of anything else. Fashion moves so quickly that, unless you have a strong point of view, you can lose integrity.\n\nYou have to always work against what you did before, and even against your taste. You have to stay true to your heritage; that\'s what your brand is about. Dressing is a way of life. I always say: <em><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; text-decoration: underline;\">To be well dressed you must be well naked. I like things simple.</span></span></em>\n\nHerb let dont fish gathering. Yielding female kind creepeth sixth youll be creature youll subdue. Fly that theyre subdue. Under appear, appear in first.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\n<h5><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-314\" src=\"https://peakshops.fuelthemes.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/ic1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"14\" />  <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Our Store</span></h5>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"6px\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">8212 E. Glen Creek Street Orchard Park, NY 14127, </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">United States of America</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"10px\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Phone: +1 909969 0383</span>\n<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Email:</span> <span style=\"color: #c0af8e; font-size: 14px;\">hello@fuelthemes.net</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"30px\"][vc_column_text]\n<h5><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-315\" src=\"https://peakshops.fuelthemes.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/ic2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" />  <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Store Hours</span></h5>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"6px\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Monday-Saturday 11am7pm ET\nSunday 11am6pm ET</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"316\"][/thb_image][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>Commitment To Quality</h2>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"24px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1582198323774{margin-bottom: 70px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\