(809, 1, '2021-06-02 19:33:15', '2021-06-02 18:33:15', '<p>[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][thb_page_menu menu=\"149\"][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">THANK YOU FOR YOUR INTEREST IN THE RELOVED RACK (TRR)</strong></p>\r\n<p>This document sets out the terms under which TRR will engage with you, the Buyer. This information is STRICTLY confidential and must not be distributed to any third party, in whole or part, without TRR\'s express permission.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">QUALITY OF ITEMS</strong></p>\r\n<p>We take utmost care in ensuring that the goods we cell meet a certain standard of quality and this includes checking for any defects, discolorations, peeling etc.</p>\r\n<p>We care for our customers and will bring only the best bargains to you at great quality. Items featured are either brand new or reasonably used preloved goods from previous owners who are decluttering. We maintain a standard of cleanliness to ensure the goods reach you in the best state possible.</p>\r\n<p>We will always disclose the condition of all goods (new or used) and defects (if any) will be highlighted. [/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">PAYMENT</strong></p>\r\n<p>Full payment validates order. Deposits may be accepted on certain items at our discretion on such terms to be agreed in writing.</p>\r\n<p>We only accept payment via electronic channels. Payment details will be provided at checkout.</p>\r\n<p>Each customer is served on a first come, first serve basis and will be given 24 hours to make payment on selected items after which the next customer indicating interest will be invited to make payment for the same item.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">STOCKPILING</strong></p>\r\n<p>TRR may hold paid stock for up to 2 weeks after which we will dispatch to the buyer. Please endeavor to receive goods as soon as payment is made.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">DELIVERY</strong></p>\r\n<p>We deliver nationwide via a multitude of logistics companies. We are amenable to using your choice of courier where required.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]<strong style=\"color: #000000;\">RETURNS &amp; REFUNDS</strong></p>\r\n<p>Returns are accepted on unworn and unused items in the same state as at the time of purchase. Cost of return will be borne by the buyer. Refund will be processed within 48 hours after assessing the returned item. We do not accept exchanges on any sold items. [/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\r\n', 'Terms & Conditions (Buyers)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '803-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-06-02 19:33:15', '2021-06-02 18:33:15', '', 803, 'https://therelovedrack.com/?p=809', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(810, 1, '2021-06-02 19:33:35', '2021-06-02 18:33:35', '<p>[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][thb_page_menu menu=\"149\"][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]Luxury pieces are an investment and we help secure your investment by guaranteeing each and every item we sell as authentic.</p>\r\n<p>Each and every piece of our inventory, especially our premium designer items, undergo rigorous internal checks as well as confirmation via 3rd party independent authentication software to give confidence on the authenticity of the item. The process we undergo starts from a thorough visual inspection of hardware, material, craftsmanship, tags, logos, lettering, purchase receipts etc. We also do a side by side comparison of the style and brand and where required, use 3rd party authentication software to give 100% authenticity.</p>\r\n<p>Only items proven authentic are accepted for resale.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\r\n', 'How We Authenticate', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '794-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-06-02 19:33:35', '2021-06-02 18:33:35', '', 794, 'https://therelovedrack.com/?p=810', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
