(697, 1, '2021-05-23 19:07:44', '2021-05-23 19:07:44', '<p>[vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1620143036019{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}\" el_class=\"align-justify\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 500;\">We are the foremost consignment store that curates preloved fashion &amp; accessories (mid-market to luxury) for the discerning woman, who celebrates her femininity through her style.<br />\r\n</span></h2>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"26px\"][vc_column_text]We are the leading consignment store based in Nigeria with an African reach. We are seeking to influence women\'s buying choices, get them to embrace a more sustainable lifestyle, and drive environmental consciousness at a time where there is a global shift away from fast fashion.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"26px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h5><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Our Store</span></h5>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"6px\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Larry Izamoje Close,<br />\r\nLekki Phase 1,<br />\r\n501102 Lagos, Nigeria</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"10px\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Phone: +234 (0) 816 585 2416</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Email:</span> <span style=\"color: #c0af8e; font-size: 14px;\">info@therelovedrack.com</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"26px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][thb_image alignment=\"aligncenter\" image=\"316\"][/thb_image][vc_empty_space height=\"50px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1582198323774{margin-bottom: 70px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"5/12\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2>Our Mission</h2>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"24px\"][vc_column_text]To change the culture around pre-owned retail in Africa by creating an elevated consignment experience.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"6px\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The Reloved Rack is about a culture shift. Our brand strategy revolves around the opportunity to educate and re-orientate the African culture around pre-loved items.</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"30px\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2>Our Vision</h2>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"24px\"][vc_column_text]To be the foremost African presence in the global shift towards consignment &amp; sustainable fashion[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"6px\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The Reloved Rack will be the go-to consignment store for quality fashion in Africa.</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"30px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"7/12\"][thb_image alignment=\"alignright\" image=\"735\"][/thb_image][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row thb_full_width=\"true\" thb_row_padding=\"true\" thb_column_padding=\"true\" css=\".vc_custom_1620145507378{margin-bottom: 50px !important;padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner el_class=\"align-center\"][vc_column_inner offset=\"vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-9\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"text-center\"]</p>\r\n<h2>Our Values</h2>\r\n<p>Our values capture our core beliefs about fashion, customer experience, lifestyle and people.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"text-center\" css=\".vc_custom_1620145173576{padding-top: 100px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 100px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;background-color: #e5f2cf !important;}\"]</p>\r\n<h5><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">QUALITY IS KING</span></h5>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">[In Fashion / In Experience]</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"text-center\" css=\".vc_custom_1620145256720{padding-top: 100px !important;padding-rig